data.description: Lovely single-story home in a quiet community in the NE that exudes charm. The spacious living room is drenched in plenty of natural light with immaculate tile floors. The modern kitchen, with its custom cabinets, sparkling granite counters & stainless steel appliances, is a convenient space to prepare gourmet meals and it overlooks the huge dining area, which is perfect for entertaining. Quiet restful nights await in the 3 bedrooms, each with crisp walls & carpeted floors. The primary bedroom boasts a walk-in closet with a modern ensuite bathroom featuring dual sinks and separate shower & tub. Enjoy drinks under the covered patio in the backyard, which is ready for your creative ideas. A private 2-car garage has plenty of space for vehicles and/or storage. The property boasts a stunning curb appeal with its "zen-like" desert landscaping. Located minutes from shopping, restaurants, schools, Bruce Woodbury Beltway & Hwy 15, come visit today!
